  "text": "Consider the non-cooperative joint power and rate control game (PRCG)Ĝ = [K, {Â k }, {u k }] where K = {1, 2, · · · , K} is the set of users,Â k = [0, P max ] × [0, B] is the strategy set for user k with a strategy corresponding to a choice of transmit power and transmit rate, and u k is the utility function for user k given by [CITATION_1] . Here, B is the system bandwidth. Each user chooses its transmit power and rate in order to maximize its own utility while satisfying its delay QoS requirements. The resulting delay-constrained power and rate control game can be expressed as",
